project.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fcast-crew-loan-outs-severe-stakes-1236018212%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fcast-crew-loan-outs-severe-stakes-1236018212%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%20a%20dozen%20GOP%20states%20seeking%20to%20block%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20through%20Biden's%20SAVE%20repayment%20plan%20may%20have%20been%20set%20back%20by%20a%20separate%20court%20ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225850%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22College%20graduation%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626c0f8cc8c8ac00194119c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20been%20using%20one-time%20account%20adjustments%20to%20give%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20targeted%20groups%20of%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Sixth%20Circuit%20rejected%20a%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20these%20account%20adjustments%2C%20saying%20it%20doesn't%20have%20standing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20separate%20ongoing%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20Biden's%20latest%20relief%20plan%20used%20the%20same%20argument.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20to%20block%20some%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20targeted%20student-debt%20relief%20efforts%20are%20simmering%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20court%20ruling%20might%20have%20signaled%20how%20one%20case%20will%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20the%20New%20Civil%20Liberties%20Alliance%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20on%20behalf%20of%20conservative%20groups%20the%20Cato%20Institute%20and%20Mackinac%20Center%20for%20Public%20Policy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-lawsuit-block-student-loan-forgiveness-income-driven-repayment-relief-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20block%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20Education%20Department's%20one-time%20account%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adjustments%20allow%20borrowers%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20and%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-idr-student-debt-relief-account-adjustment-biden-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20additional%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20their%20payment%20counts%20evaluated%2C%20potentially%20giving%20them%20more%20credit%20toward%20loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative%20groups%20argued%20that%20the%20adjustments%20were%20unconstitutional%20and%2C%20as%20nonprofits%2C%20undermined%20their%20recruiting%20efforts%20toward%20PSLF%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20an%20agency%20arbitrarily%20reduces%20the%20financial%20incentive%20for%20student-loan%20debtors%20to%20seek%20and%20remain%20in%20jobs%20with%20public%20service%20employers%2C%20at%20any%20given%20wage%2C%20the%20supply%20of%20workers%20willing%20to%20take%20and%20keep%20jobs%20with%20such%20employers%20inevitably%20falls%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20groups%20wrote%20in%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit%20wasn't%20convinced.%20On%20May%2017%2C%20it%20rejected%20the%20groups'%20appeal%2C%20writing%20in%20its%20decision%20that%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20account%20adjustment%20will%20reduce%20the%20appeal%20of%20PSLF%20is%20%26quot%3Bunconvincing%20and%20illogical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiffs%20have%20not%20alleged%20that%20any%20of%20their%20employees%20have%20stopped%20seeking%20PSLF%20forgiveness%20because%20of%20the%20adjustment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court's%20decision%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20without%20supporting%20facts%2C%20the%20claim%20is%20pure%20conjecture%2C%20not%20enough%20to%20show%20a%20competitive%20injury.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ongoing%20separate%20lawsuit%20had%20the%20same%20argument%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20different%20program.%20In%20March%2C%2011%20GOP%20state%20attorneys%20general%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-save-plan-lawsuit-gop-attorneys-general-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20block%20the%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20Education%20Department%20implemented%20last%20summer%20to%20give%20borrowers%20more%20affordable%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20additional%20GOP%20attorneys%20general%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-states-lawsuit-block-save-student-loan-income-driven-repayment-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20SAVE%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20new%20repayment%20plan%20diminishes%20the%20value%20of%20PSLF%20and%20harms%20the%20states'%20efforts%20to%20recruit%20people%20to%20the%20public%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden's%20Education%20Department%20filed%20a%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20Friday%2C%20citing%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit's%20decision%20to%20reject%20the%20New%20Civil%20Lebrties%20Alliances's%20argument%20that%20the%20account%20adjustments%20would%20hurt%20the%20nonprofits'%20PSLF%20recruitment%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiffs%20offer%20the%20examples%20of%20hypothetical%20current%20and%20prospective%20employees%20and%20predict%2C%20based%20on%20'the%20concept%20of%20economic%20incentives%2C'%20how%20they%20might%20act.%20Economic%20assumptions%20alone%20were%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit%2C%20nor%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Education%20Department%20wrote%20in%20its%20legal%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20base%2C%20career-related%20decisions%20are%20complicated%2C%20and%20PSLF%20is%20not%20the%20sole%20incentive%20in%20this%20economic%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department%20added.%20%26quot%3BPlaintiffs%20would%20have%20Defendants%20and%20the%20Court%20sort%20out%20this%20complexity%20on%20their%20behalf.%20But%20standing%20is%20their%20burden%20alone%2C%20and%20they%20have%20not%20carried%20it%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20when%20the%20court%20will%20rule%20on%20the%20lawsuits%20to%20block%20SAVE%2C%20but%20given%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit's%20ruling%20on%20the%20prior%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20Biden's%20account%20adjustments%2C%20it%20could%20signal%20how%20judges%20are%20considering%20opponents'%20arguments%20to%20block%20targeted%20student-debt%20relief%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-student-loan-forgiveness-gop-state-lawsuit-setback-sixth-circuit-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717006595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61e975a27c6a20001842b7c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-student-loan-forgiveness-gop-state-lawsuit-setback-sixth-circuit-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20ruling%20in%20a%20separate%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20student-debt%20relief%20could%20suggest%20how%20the%20court%20might%20rule%20on%20GOP%20states'%20argument%20to%20block%20the%20SAVE%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-student-loan-forgiveness-gop-state-lawsuit-setback-sixth-circuit-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MTNL%20Q4%20results%3A%20Net%20loss%20widens%20to%20Rs%20817%20cr%20on%20high%20finance%20costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717006447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs