fference%20lies%20in%20the%20steel.%20This%20KitchenAid%20knife%20uses%20AUS-10%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20high-carbon%20Japanese%20steel%20that%20is%20just%20a%20little%20less%20durable%20than%20Shun's%20proprietary%20VG-MAX%20blend.%20All%20this%20means%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20be%20more%20diligent%20about%20checking%20and%20maintaining%20the%20edge%20of%20KitchenAid's%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20partial%20tang%20construction%20makes%20it%20relatively%20lightweight%20at%20eight%20ounces.%20Between%20the%20handle%20and%20the%20blade%20is%20an%20integrated%20bolster%20that%20keeps%20the%20knife%20balanced.%20The%20wooden%20handle%20is%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20in%20both%20small%20and%20larger%20hands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20sharpest%20knives%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20Though%20there%20was%20slight%20resistance%20working%20through%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20the%20knife%20retained%20a%20sharp%20edge%20and%20was%20able%20to%20slice%20through%20tomatoes%20like%20butter.%20It%20made%20quick%20work%20of%20cutting%20through%20vegetables%20and%20herbs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20professional%5C%22%3EBest%20professional%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20professional%20kitchens%20are%20home%20to%20W%C3%BCsthof%20knives%20because%20these%20knives%20are%20workhorses%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20The%20W%C3%BCsthof%20Classic%208-inch%20Chef's%20Knife%20is%20crafted%20from%20a%20synthetic%20polyoxymethylene%20handle%20with%20a%20high-carbon%20stainless%20steel%20blade%3B%20this%20full-tang%20knife%20is%20as%20sturdy%20as%20they%20come.%20The%20heavier%20weight%20and%20sharp%20edge%20help%20to%20move%20through%20tougher%20foods%20such%20as%20sweet%20potatoes%20with%20ease.%20During%20our%20tests%2C%20we%20sliced%20thin%20slices%20of%20tomatoes%20with%20hardly%20any%20resistance%20and%20easily%20chopped%20through%20parsley%20without%20any%20mashing%20of%20the%20herb.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2