ef's%20Knife%20on%20a%20cutting%20board%20surrounded%20by%20sliced%20sweet%20potatoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66576e75d0b8e1c832c9ea28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrior%20to%20each%20of%20the%20tests%20performed%2C%20the%20best%20chef's%20knives%20were%20rinsed%20or%20washed%20by%20hand%20and%20dried.%3Cp%3EMolly%20Allen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaper%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20cut%20through%20regular%20printer%20paper%20to%20assess%20the%20knife's%20blade%20and%20sharpness%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20packaging.%20This%20same%20test%20was%20performed%20after%20using%20the%20knife%20for%20multiple%20tasks%20to%20evaluate%20edge%20retention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECutting%20performance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20used%20the%20knives%20to%20mince%20parsley%20to%20see%20if%20the%20blade%20produced%20fine%20cuts%20and%20did%20not%20pulverize%20the%20herbs.%20Then%2C%20we%20sliced%20tomatoes%2C%20ensuring%20they%20could%20cut%20through%20the%20fragile%20flesh%20smoothly%20and%20without%20crushing%20it.%20We%20chopped%20through%20sweet%20potatoes%20with%20the%20skins%20left%20on%2C%20giving%20us%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20performance%20with%20tough%20foods.%20All%20tests%20were%20performed%20on%20a%20wooden%20cutting%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Throughout%20testing%2C%20we%20paid%20specific%20attention%20to%20how%20easy%20the%20knife%20was%20to%20use%2C%20how%20comfortable%20it%20was%20to%20hold%2C%20and%20any%20other%20notable%20features.%20We%20evaluated%20each%20knife's%20blade%20and%20handle%2C%20along%20with%20blade%20hardness%20and%20angle%2C%20to%20see%20if%20these%20affected%20performances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Caring%20for%20chef's%20knives%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20care%20for%20a%20chef's%20knife%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20impor