to%20do%20a%20virtual%20walk-through%20of%20the%20cliffside%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20maybe%20all%20these%20maps%20still%20aren't%20quite%20visual%20enough%20for%20you.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20search%20up%20the%20cliffs%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-reverse-image-search%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Images%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20stunning%20photographs%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20mapping%20tools%20also%20don't%20end%20with%20Google%20Maps%20and%20Google%20Earth.%20Google%20also%20owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-waze%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20navigation%20and%20traffic%20app%20geared%20specifically%20to%20drivers%2C%20which%20offers%20realtime%20updates%20on%20traffic%20conditions%20and%20route%20hazards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Google%20Maps%2C%20Waze%20is%20a%20GPS%20tool%20that%20can%20get%20you%20from%20A%20to%20B%20and%20offer%20multiple%20routes.%20But%20unlike%20Google%20Maps%2C%20Waze%20has%20a%20community-based%20component%2C%20allowing%20drivers%20to%20report%20things%20like%20bad%20weather%2C%20accidents%2C%20and%20other%20traffic%20conditions%20to%20alert%20other%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fefb95b2-428d-4bef-bf6f-cf5b177413cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20use%20Google%20Street%20View%20on%20desktop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Maps%20works%20on%20both%20your%20desktop%2C%20and%20mobile%20device.%C2%A0Here's%20how%20to%20get%20to%20Street%20View%20on%20your%20computer%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EGo%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmaps.google.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaps.google.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETap%20the%20search%20bar%20in%20the%20top-left%20corner%20of%20the%20screen%20and%20enter%20the%20name%20or%20address%20of%20the%20place%20that%20you%20want%20to%20view.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EClick%20and%20hold%20the%20person%20icon%20in%20the%20bottom-right%20corner%20of%20the%20screen%20and%20drag%20it%20to%20the%20spot%20you%20want%20to%20view%20(as%20you%20move%20the%20cursor%20over%20the%20map%2C%20the%20streets%20will%20be%20highlighted%20in%20blue%20%E2%80%94%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20place%20the%20icon%20onto%20one%20of%20those%2C%20otherwise%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20street%20view).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Central%20Park%20on%20Google%20Maps%20shows%20a%20red%20box%20and%20red%20arrow%20emphasizing%20the%20icon%20of%20a%20yellow%20figure%2C%20representing%20Google%20Street%20View.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66562029239fda2da6cc3776%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221982%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20see%20what%20a%20location%20looks%20like%20on%20Google%20Street%20View%2C%20click%20and%20drag%20the%20yellow%20icon.%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Mark%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERelease%20the%20cursor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20navigate%20in%20street%20view%2C%20click%20and%20drag%20to%20change%20the%20camera%20angle%20or%20tap%20a%20location%20down%20the%20street%20to%20move%20closer%20to%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20the%20curved%20arrows%20around%20the%20compass%20icon%20in%20the%20bottom-left%20corner%20of%20the%20screen%20to%20change%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20on%20Google%20Street%20View%20are%20updated%20once%20every%20one%20to%20three%20years%2C%20but%20well-known%20places%20are%20updated%20more%20frequently.%20You%20can%20check%20the%20date%20of%20a%20Street%20View%20image%20by%20looking%20for%20the%20date%20in%20the%20black%20box%20at%20the%20top%20left-hand%20side%20of%20the%20screen%2C%20or%20on%20the%20bar%20on%20the%20bottom%20right-hand%20side%20of%20the%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D