Mark%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20navigate%20on%20the%20mobile%20version%20of%20Google%20Street%20View%2C%20drag%20one%20finger%20across%20the%20screen%2C%20starting%20on%20the%20side%20you%20want%20to%20go%20toward%20and%20ending%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ab78090-6eaa-4b7f-889e-429650891a67%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20blur%20my%20house%20on%20Google%20Maps%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Street%20View%20may%20potentially%20reveal%20more%20than%20you'd%20like%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20your%20house%20has%20distinctive%20features%2C%20or%20there's%20a%20large%20window%20with%20a%20view%20directly%20into%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20concerns%20about%20privacy%20or%20safety%2C%20there%20is%20a%20solution.%20You%20can%20request%20Google%20to%20blur%20your%20house%20permanently%2C%20leaving%20behind%20only%20a%20vague%20outline%20of%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20to%20do%20it%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EGo%20to%20Google%20Maps%20and%20enter%20your%20home%20address.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEnter%20into%20%3Cstrong%3EStreet%20View%20mode%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20dragging%20the%20small%20yellow%20human-shaped%20icon%20at%20the%20bottom-right%20corner%20of%20the%20screen%20onto%20the%20map%20in%20front%20of%20your%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20your%20house%20in%20view%2C%20click%20%26quot%3BReport%20a%20problem%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20bottom-right%20corner%20of%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECenter%20the%20red%20box%20on%20your%20home%2C%20and%20select%20%26quot%3BMy%20home%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BRequest%20blurring%26quot%3B%20field.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20shows%20Google%20Maps'%20page%20to%20report%20an%20inappropriate%20street%20view%2C%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BMy%20home%26quot%3B%20option%20selected%20and%20emphasized%20with%20a%20r