ere%20was%20a%20chance%20the%20police%20might%20be%20pressured.%20I%20told%20him%20not%20to%20succumb%20to%20any%20political%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCP%20leader%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20activist%20claiming%20that%20the%20calls%20were%20made%20to%20favour%20the%20accused%20and%20demanding%20that%20his%20phone%20records%20be%20checked%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20in%20Marathi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20ready%20for%20a%20narco%20test%20but%2C%20if%20I%20am%20cleared%2C%20you%20(Ms%20Damania)%20should%20stay%20quiet%20at%20home%20and%20take%20%3Cem%3E'sanyas'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Is%20she%20ready%20for%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColleagues%20In%20Dock%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20dean%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20-%20%C2%A0where%20two%20doctors%20were%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20replacing%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20them%20-%20claimed%20that%20a%20minister%20and%20an%20MLA%20from%20Mr%20Pawar's%20party%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20asking%20for%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20to%20be%20made%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forensics%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vinayak%20Kale%20claimed%20that%20the%20letter%20was%20written%20by%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20and%20MLA%20Sunil%20Tingre%20in%20favour%20of%20Dr%20Ajay%20Tawade%2C%20who%20was%20suspended%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20hospital's%20Forensic%20Medicine%20Department%20on%20Wednesday%20.%20Mr%20Tingre%20is%20already%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20for%20visiting%20the%20police%20station%20where%20the%20teenager%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20accident%20on%20May%2019%20to%20allegedly%20pressure%20officials%20into%20going%20easy%20on%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kale%20was%20later