20borrowing%20costs.%20In%202014%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20upped%20India's%20outlook%20to%20stable%20from%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20positive%20outlook%20on%20India%20is%20predicated%20on%20its%20robust%20economic%20growth%2C%20pronounced%20improvement%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20government%20spending%2C%20and%20political%20commitment%20to%20fiscal%20consolidation.%20We%20believe%20these%20factors%20are%20coalescing%20to%20benefit%20credit%20metrics%2C%26quot%3B%20S%26amp%3BP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrrespective%20of%20the%20June%202024%20general%20election%20results%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20expects%20the%20incoming%20government%20to%20carry%20on%20economic%20reforms%20to%20support%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20vigor%26quot%3B%2C%20continued%20infrastructure%20investment%20drive%2C%20and%20commitment%20to%20fiscal%20consolidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20a%20rating%20upgrade%20on%20the%20back%20of%20improved%20fiscal%20management%20and%20strong%20economic%20fundamentals%2C%20including%20high%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP's%20rating%20commentary%20comes%20within%20a%20week%20of%20RBI's%20record%20Rs%202.10%20lakh%20crore%20dividend%20transfer%20to%20the%20government.%20The%20funds%20may%20be%20used%20to%20reduce%20the%20Centre's%20fiscal%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20hopes%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20to%205.1%25%20of%20GDP%20by%20March%202025%20and%20further%20to%204.5%25%20by%20March%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20sound%20economic%20fundamentals%20to%20underpin%20the%20growth%20momentum%20over%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20we%20expect%20broad%20continuity%20in%20economic%20reforms%20and%20fiscal%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20S%26amp%3BP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20composition%20of%20government%20spending%20has%20been%20transformed%2C%20with%20an%20increasing%20share%20going%20to%20infrastructure.%20This%20will%20ease%20bottlenecks%20to%20put%20the%20country%20on%20a%20higher%20growth%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20said%20India's%20robust%20economic%20expansion%20is%20having%20a%20constructive%20impact%20on%20its%20credit%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20sound%20economic%20fundamentals%20to%20underpin%20the%20growth%20momentum%20over%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20we%20expect%20broad%20continuity%20in%20economic%20reforms%20and%20fiscal%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20S%26amp%3BP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20outlook%20reflects%20S%26amp%3BP's%20view%20that%20continued%20policy%20stability%2C%20deepening%20economic%20reforms%2C%20and%20high%20infrastructure%20investment%20will%20sustain%20long-term%20growth%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%2C%20along%20with%20cautious%20fiscal%20and%20monetary%20policy%20that%20diminishes%20the%20government's%20elevated%20debt%20and%20interest%20burden%20while%20bolstering%20economic%20resilience%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20higher%20rating%20over%20the%20next%2024%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20S%26amp%3BP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20rating%20action%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20enthuse%20the%20stock%20market%20with%20BSE%20Sensex%20falling%20667.55%20points%20to%2074%2C502.90.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20said%20the%20Indian%20economy%20has%20staged%20a%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%20comeback%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20It%20forecasts%20India's%20real%20GDP%20growth%20at%206.8%25%20this%20year%2C%20which%20compares%20favourably%20with%20emerging%20market%20peers%20amid%20a%20broad%20global%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20estimates%20real%20GDP%20growth%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%20to%20have%20averaged%208.1%25%20annually%2C%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20expects%20these%20growth%20dynamics%20to%20continue%20to%20play%20out%20in%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20with%20GDP%20expanding%20close%20to%207%25%20annually%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20which%20will%20have%20a%20moderating%20effect%20on%20the%20ratio%20of%20government%20debt%20to%20GDP%20despite%20still%20wide%20fiscal%20deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20said%20the%20quality%20of%20government%20spending%20has%20improved%20in%20the%20past%20four%20to%20five%20years%20and%20public%20investment%20and%20consumer%20momentum%20will%20underpin%20solid%20growth%20prospects%20over%20the%20next%20three%20to%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20administration%20has%20increasingly%20shifted%20budget%20allocation%20to%20infrastructure%20spending.%20Capital%20expenditure%20is%20scheduled%20to%20increase%20to%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20crore%2C%20or%20about%203.4%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20fiscal%202025.%20This%20is%20almost%204.5x%20from%20a%20decade%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20believes%20that%20the%20improvements%20in%20infrastructure%20and%20connectivity%20in%20India%20will%20remove%20chokepoints%2C%20which%20are%20hindering%20long-term%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20weak%20fiscal%20settings%20had%20always%20been%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20part%20of%20its%20sovereign%20ratings%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20major%20global%20rating%20agencies%20--%20S%26amp%3BP%2C%20Fitch%2C%20and%20Moody's%20--%20have%20accorded%20the%20lowest%20investment%20grade%20rating%20to%20India.%20Fitch%20and%20Moody's%20still%20have%20a%20stable%20outlook%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20said%20it%20may%20raise%20the%20ratings%20if%20India's%20fiscal%20deficit%20narrows%20meaningfully%20such%20that%20the%20general%20government%20debt%20falls%20below%207%25%20of%20GDP%20on%20a%20structural%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20also%20raise%20the%20ratings%20if%20we%20observe%20a%20sustained%20and%20substant