0on%20two%204%2C000-year-old%20skulls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20be%20the%20place%20of%20one%20of%20the%20early%20civilisations%2C%20ancient%20Egyptians%20have%20been%20known%20to%20identify%2C%20describe%2C%20and%20treat%20diseases%20and%20traumatic%20injuries%2C%20build%20prostheses%2C%20and%20put%20in%20dental%20fillings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20their%20further%20prowess%2C%20an%20international%20team%20of%20researchers%20studied%20two%20human%20skulls%20--%20male%20and%20female%20and%20each%20thousands%20of%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cut%20marks%20on%20the%20skulls%20revealed%20the%20extent%20of%20traumatological%20and%20oncological%20treatments%20practised%20by%20the%20ancient%20Egyptians%2C%20they%20said%20in%20the%20paper%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Frontiers%20in%20Medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdgard%20Camaros%2C%20a%20paleopathologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Santiago%20de%20Compostela%20in%20Spain%20called%20the%20discovery%20%26quot%3Bunique%20and%20extraordinary%26quot%3B%20evidence%20of%20how%20ancient%20Egyptian%20medicine%20would%20have%20tried%20to%20deal%20with%20or%20explore%20cancer%20more%20than%204%2C000%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%3EUn%20estudo%20liderado%20pola%20USC%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEdgard_Camaros%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Edgard_Camaros%3C%2Fa%3E)%20revela%20posibles%20intentos%20de%20tratar%20o%20cancro%20nun%20cranio%20exipcio%20de%204.000%20anos.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk4qfk9bha4%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk4qfk9bha4%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fwk2Qvh9zvR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fwk2Qvh9zvR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20USC%20(%40UniversidadeUSC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUniversidadeUSC%2Fstatus%2F1795709207423135845%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20skulls%20--%20Skull%20and%20Mandible%20236%2C%20dating%20from%20between%202687%20and%202345%20BCE%2C%20belonged%20to%20a%20male%20individual%20aged%2030%20to%2035%2C%20while%20Skull%20E270%2C%20dating%20from%20between%20663%20and%20343%20BCE%2C%20belonged%20to%20a%20female%20individual%20who%20was%20older%20than%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicroscopic%20observation%20of%20skull%20236%20showed%20a%20big-sized%20lesion%20consistent%20with%20excessive%20tissue%20destruction%2C%20known%20as%20neoplasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20there%20were%20also%2030%20or%20so%20small%20and%20round%20metastasised%20lesions%20scattered%20across%20the%20skull%2C%20with%20cut%20marks%20probably%20made%20by%20a%20sharp%20object%20such%20as%20a%20metal%20instrument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20first%20observed%20the%20cut%20marks%20under%20the%20microscope%2C%20we%20could%20not%20believe%20what%20was%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tatiana%20Tondini%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tubingen%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysis%20of%20Skull%20E270%20also%20showed%20a%20big%20lesion%20consistent%20with%20a%20cancerous%20tumour%20that%20led%20to%20bone%20destruction%2C%20and%20two%20lesions%20from%20traumatic%20injuries%20that%20received%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20may%20indicate%20that%20although%20today's%20lifestyle%20and%20cancer-causing%20substances%20in%20the%20environment%20increase%20cancer%20risk%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20common%20pathology%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716997560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7mi3bipo_ancient-egypt-cancer-treatment_