0Saxena%20to%20%26quot%3Bgive%20up%20negativity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVK%20Saxena%20directed%20that%20the%20three-hour%20break%20for%20labourers%20has%20been%20implemented%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20since%20May%2020%20and%20will%20continue%20across%20all%20sites%20till%20temperatures%20come%20down%20below%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20according%20to%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20by%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20Lt%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20Delhi%20is%20facing%20an%20unprecedented%20heatwave%20with%20temperatures%20hovering%20around%2050%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20some%20parts%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20city's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Mungeshpur%20area%20logged%20a%20maximum%20of%2052.3%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20temperature%20recorded%20in%20the%20city%2C%20while%20Delhi's%20primary%20weather%20station%20Safdarjung%20Observatory%20recorded%20a%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2046.8%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20the%20highest%20in%2079%20years%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOrdinarily%2C%20he%20(VK%20Saxena)%20expected%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20the%20concerned%20minister%20would%20convene%20a%20meeting%20for%20a%20heat%20action%20plan%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20and%20seriousness%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20heat%20wave%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20L-G%20had%20instructed%20the%20DDA%20on%20May%2020%20to%20make%20adequate%20arrangements%20for%20providing%20water%20and%20coconut%20water%20to%20labourers%20at%20construction%20sites%20so%20that%20they%20can%20stay%20hydrated%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20VK%20Saxena%20said%20the%20chief%20secretary%20may%20immediately%20call%20a%20meeting%20of%20officers%20from%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%2C%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20Irrigation%20and%20Flood%20Control%20Department%2C%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%2C%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%2C%20Power%20Department%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Urban%20Shelter%20Improvement%20Board%20and%20issue%20necessary%20directions%20for%20protecting%20labourers%20and%20supervisory%20staff%20from%20extreme%20heat%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20directed%20that%20earthen%20pots%20with%20drinking%20water%20should%20be%20arranged%20at%20bus%20shelters%2C%20treated%20water%20from%20STPs%20be%20sprinkled%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20and%20water%20sprinklers%20installed%20at%20high-rise%20buildings%20be%20activated%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20ambient%20air%20temperature%20and%20tackle%20pollution%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20said%2C%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20poor%20labourers%2C%20who%20toil%20relentlessly%20in%20sweltering%20heat%20warrants%20a%20humane%20approach%20of%20administration.%20Thousands%20of%20homeless%20people%20and%20street%20vendors%20who%20spend%20their%20day%20on%20the%20footpaths%2C%20sometimes%20with%20babies%20without%20access%20to%20drinking%20water%2C%20is%20a%20heart-rending%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20the%20letter%20written%20by%20the%20L-G's%20office%20was%20spreading%20falsehood%20and%20he%20shared%20a%20clip%20of%20a%20news%20conference%20that%20he%20addressed%20on%20Monday%20wherein%20he%20explained%20the%20AAP%20government's%20action%20plan%20to%20tackle%20the%20heatwave%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20press%20briefing%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20two%20beds%20each%20at%2026%20hospitals%20and%20five%20at%20Delhi%20government-run%20LNJP%20hospital%20were%20being%20kept%20reserved%20for%20heat%20stroke%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directions%20to%20tackle%20heat%20wave%20will%20be%20implemented%20across%20all%20construction%20sites%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20those%20of%20government%20agencies%20and%20private%20establishments%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Labour%20Department%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20in%20an%20advisory%20issued%20on%20Monday%2C%20listed%20the%20various%20measures%20needed%20amid%20the%20heatwave%20conditions%20prevailing%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20asked%20establishments%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20clean%20drinking%20water%20availability%20at%20the%20workplace%2C%20availability%20of%20coolers%2Ffans%20at%20the%20workplace%20and%20proper%20ventilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20also%20said%20no%20worker%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20work%20in%20direct%20exposure%20to%20sunlight%2C%20and%20advised%20a%20change%20in%20the%20shift%20of%20work%20as%20far%20as%20possible%20to%20avoid%20peak%20hours%20between%2012%20noon%20to%204%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensitising%20the%20workers%20about%20precautions%20to%20be%20taken%20during%20the%20heatwave%20conditions%20including%20covering%20their%20heads%20during%20direct%20exposure%20to%20sunlight%2C%20availability%20of%20emergency%20kits%20having%20ice%20packs%2C%20oral%20rehydration%20solution%20sachets%20and%20other%20items%20were%20prescribed%20in%20the%20advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716996600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F002u08u_delhi-heatwave-_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-vk-saxena-orders-paid-breaks-for-labourers-as-delhi-shatters-heat-record-5772529%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Delhi%20sizzling%20under%20an%20intense%20heatwave%2C%20Lt%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20directed%20that%20a%20paid%20break%20from%20noon%20to%203%20pm%20be%20given%20to%20labourers%2C%20along%20with%20water%20and%20coconut%20milk%20at%20construction%20sites.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-vk-saxena-orders-paid-breaks-for-labourers-as-delhi-shatters-heat-record-5772529%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-vk-saxena-orders-paid-breaks-for-labourers-as-delhi-shatters-heat-record-5772529%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-vk-saxena-orders-paid-breaks-for-labourers-as-delhi-shatters-heat-record-5772529%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20Certificates%20Under%20CAA%20Given%20To%20Beneficiaries%20In%20Bengal%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20first%20set%20of%20citizenship%20certificates%20were%20issued%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%20the%20process%20has%20also%20begun%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue.%20The%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20Empowered%20Committees%20of%20the%20States%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Uttarakhand%20have%20also%20granted%20citizenship%20to%20the%20first%20set%20of%20applicants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20was%20enacted%20in%20December%202019%20to%20grant%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20It%20reduced%20the%20qualification%20period%20for%20Hindus%2C%20Jains%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Parsis%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20came%20to%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20from%20eleven%20years%20to%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20rules%20were%20notified%20only%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20however%2C%20after%20massive%20protests%20stalled%20its%20implementation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20election%20speeches%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20attacked%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20are%20flourishing%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20party's%20rule.%20He%20repeated%20the%20charge%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demography%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20Bengal%20is%20being%20changed.%20The%20TMC%20is%20against%20giving%20citizenship%20to%20religiously%20persecuted%20minorities.%20Why%20are%20they%20opposing%20the%20CAA%20so%20much%3F%20Why%20are%20these%20people%20(TMC%20leaders)%20lying%20about%20the%20CAA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bengal's%20Kakdwip%2C%20his%20last%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20party%20does%20not%20want%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Matua%20community%20to%20stay%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20PM%20added%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BTo%20appease%20a%20section%20of%20the%20society%2C%20the%20TMC%20government%20is%20openly%20attacking%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20has%20given%20reservations%20to%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20castes.%20Reservations%20were%20looted%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20false%20OBC%20certificates%20were%20issued%20to%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20sacrifice%20her%20life%26quot%3B%20but%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20politics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20such%20as%20the%20CAA%2C%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Metiabruz%20in%20the%20Diamond%20Harbour%20constituency%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20she%20reiterated%20she%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20implement