ss-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-levies-rs-36-38-lakh-penalty-on-hsbc-for-fema-violations-124052901660_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20central%20bank%20said%20reporting%20requirements%20under%20the%20Liberalised%20Remittance%20Scheme%20of%20FEMA%2C%201999%20were%20not%20followed%20by%20HSBC%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-levies-rs-36-38-lakh-penalty-on-hsbc-for-fema-violations-124052901660_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-levies-rs-36-38-lakh-penalty-on-hsbc-for-fema-violations-124052901660_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcentral-bank-levies-rs-36-38-lakh-penalty-on-hsbc-for-fema-violations-124052901660_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20China%20Is%20Helping%20Pakistan%20In%20PoK%20With%20Military%20Supplies%20Along%20LoC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20key%20ally%20China%20has%20been%20actively%20bolstering%20the%20defence%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%20which%20includes%20the%20construction%20of%20steelhead%20bunkers%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20and%20Combat%20Aerial%20Vehicles%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20assistance%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20or%20PoK%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20installation%20of%20highly%20encrypted%20communication%20towers%20and%20the%20laying%20of%20underground%20fibre%20cables%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20advanced%20radar%20systems%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%20such%20as%20the%20'JY'%20and%20'HGR'%20series%2C%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20enhance%20medium%20and%20low%20altitude%20target%20detection%20capabilities%2C%20providing%20crucial%20intelligence%20support%20for%20army%20and%20air%20defence%20units%2C%20officials%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20SH-15%2C%20a%20155%20mm%20truck-mounted%20howitzer%20gun%20manufactured%20by%20a%20Chinese%20firm%2C%20has%20been%20noticed%20at%20various%20locations%20along%20the%20LoC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20is%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20China's%20ties%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20safeguard%20Chinese%20investments%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%2C%20particularly%20related%20to%20the%20so-called%20'China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor'%20or%20'CPEC'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20presence%20of%20senior%20PLA%20officials%20at%20forward%20posts%2C%20as%20was%20detected%20in%202014%2C%20was%20not%20found%2C%20some%20intercepts%20suggested%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20and%20engineers%20were%20setting%20up%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20LoC%2C%20including%20building%20underground%20bunkers%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20experts%20were%20engaged%20in%20tunnel%20construction%20in%20the%20Leepa%20Valley%20of%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%2C%20signalling%20preparations%20for%20an%20all-weather%20road%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Karakoram%20highway%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategic%20move%20is%20linked%20to%20Beijing's%20ambitious%2046-billion-dollar%20so-called%20'CPEC'%20project%2C%20aiming%20to%20establish%20a%20direct%20route%20between%20Gwadar%20Port%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Xinjiang%2C%20occupied%20by%20China%2C%20through%20the%20Karakoram%20highway%2C%20an%20area%20under%20the%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20a%20Chinese%20telecom%20company%20had%20taken%20over%20a%20Pakistani%20telecom%20company%20and%20formed%20China%20Mobile%20Pakistan%20(CMPak)%20-%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20China%20Mobile%20Communications%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Telecommunication%20Authority%20(PTA)%2C%20while%20renewing%20the%20mobile%20licence%20of%20CMPak%20(Zong)%20for%20PoK%2C%20gave%20permission%20to%20expand%20Next%20Generation%20Mobile%20Services%20(NGMS)%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20maintained%20silence%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20intelligence%20agencies%20are%20reportedly%20being%20kept%20informed%20of%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20continuous%20presence%20of%20Chinese%20military%20personnel%20in%20the%20region%20has%20raised%20concerns%2C%20with%20India%20voicing%20objections%20to%20Chinese%20activities%20in%20Gilgit%20and%20Baltistan%20areas%20in%20PoK%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tensions%20persist%2C%20India%20remains%20vigilant%20and%20prepared%20to%20thwart%20any%20potential%20threats%20emanating%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%20officials%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716993660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fi3hf8gi8_xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_22_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with-military-supplies-along-loc-report-5770916%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20key%20ally%20China%20has%20been%20actively%20bolstering%20the%20defence%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with