dard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fconsulting-firm-pwc-to-be-largest-customer-of-openai-s-enterprise-product-124052901669_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fconsulting-firm-pwc-to-be-largest-customer-of-openai-s-enterprise-product-124052901669_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhu%20Chopra%20calls%20SRK-Akshay%20both%20'businessman'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716992876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110540157%2Cimgsize-55066.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopras-mom-madhu-chopra-calls-salman-khan-true-gentleman-says-shah-rukh-khan-and-akshay-kumar-are-both-businessman%2Farticleshow%2F110540157.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110540157.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMadhu%20Chopra%20recently%20shared%20her%20views%20on%20Bollywood%20figures%2C%20likening%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar%20to%20'businessmen.'%20She%20praised%20Amitabh%20Bachchan's%20respect%2C%20Salman%20Khan's%20gentleness%2C%20Ranveer%20Singh's%20jovial%20nature%2C%20and%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20filial%20devotion.%20Madhu%20dismissed%20concerns%20over%20Priyanka%20Chopra's%20age%20gap%20with%20Nick%20Jonas%2C%20emphasizing%20their%20love%20and%20happiness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopras-mom-madhu-chopra-calls-salman-khan-true-gentleman-says-shah-rukh-khan-and-akshay-kumar-are-both-businessman%2Farticleshow%2F110540157.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Got%20Death%20Threats%20For%20Criticising%20Kohli%3A%20IPL%20Commentator%2C%20Karthik%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Zealand%20pacer%20Simon%20Doull%20has%20revealed%20that%20he%20has%20been%20receiving%20death%20threats%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20India%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20has%20often%20labelled%20Kohli%20as%20the%20greatest%20batter%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20he%20also%20doesn't%20shy%20away%20from%20criticising%20him%20whenever%20he%20needs%20to.%20As%20an%20observer%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Doull%20was%20one%20of%20several%20former%20players%20who%20had%20criticised%20Kohli%20for%20his%20batting%20strike%20rate%20during%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20had%20also%20voiced%20his%20anger%20over%20the%20criticism%20of%20his%20batting%20approach%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20doesn't%20like%20people%20to%20tell%20him%20how%20to%20construct%20him%2C%20considering%20that%20he%20has%20been%20winning%20games%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20RCB's%20wait%20for%20an%20IPL%20title%20continued%2C%20Kohli%20ended%20the%20season%20as%20the%20highest%20run-getter.%20He%20scored%20741%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%20154.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20discussion%2C%20Kohli's%20RCB%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dinesh%20Karthik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F666-dinesh-karthik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDinesh%20Karthik%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20star%20batter%20thrives%20in%20such%20situations%20as%20he%20likes%20to%20prove%20his%20critics%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20would%20like%20to%20write%20a%20book%20on%20how%20he%20was%20this%20year.%20He%20started%20okay.%20Thanks%20to%20people%20like%20Simon%20(Doull)%20and%20a%20few%20others%20who%20really%20spurred%20him%20on.%20And%20you%20know%20that%20side%20of%20Virat%20Kohli.%20I%20think%20that%20he%20thrives%20on%20that.%20He%20is%20someone%20who%20inadvertently%20holds%20on%20to%20certain%20things%20to%20do%20well.%20He%20loves%20people%20proving%20wrong.%20Even%20though%20he%20might%20not%20come%20out%20and%20say%20this%2C%20it%20really%20fuels%20his%20passion.%20He%20is%20like%20a%20molten%20lava%20coming%20out.%20He%20is%20fiery%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20anywhere%20close%20to%20him%20because%20you%20are%20going%20to%20get%20burnt%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20Karthik%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3PeYKSPdjm0%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20IPL%202024%20final%20with%20Doull%20also%20part%20of%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoull%20emphasised%20that%20nobody%20really%20cares%20when%20he%20praises%20Kohli%2C%20but%20a%20minor%20criticism%20of%20the%20star%20batter%20often%20leads%20to%20him%20getting%20death%20threats%20from%20the%20so%20called%20fans%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20too%20good%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20if%20he%20gets%20out.%20He's%20too%20good%20a%20player%2C%20and%20that%20was%20always%20my%20point%20around%20him.%20I%20said%20a%20thousand%20great%20things%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20but%20I%20say%20one%20thing%20that%20might%20be%20slightly%20negative%20or%20construed%20to%20be%20negative%2C%20I%20get%20death%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Doull%20pointed%20out%20during%20the%20same%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoull%20further%20suggested%20that%20he%20has%20nothing%20personal%20against%20Kohli%20as%20he%20often%20speaks%20to%20him%20before%20or%20after%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20personal.%20We've%20had%20great%20conversations.%20I've%20interviewed%20him%20at%20tosses%2C%20we've%20talked%20after%20games%2C%20there's%20never%20been%20an%20issue.%20It's%20the%20same%20thing%20I%20said%20about%20Babar%20and%20talked%20to%20him%20after%20the%20game.%20He%20also%20told%20me%20that%20the%20coach%20had%20said%20that%20same%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%20condemned%20the%20death%20threats%20against%20Doull%2C%20urging%20the%20Indian%20fans%20to%20find%20the%20difference%20between%20constructive%20criticism%20and%20someone%20taking%20personal%20jibes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20pretty%20sad%20to%20hear%20though...You%20go%20to%20basketball%2C%20football%20games%20and%20you%20see%20pundits%20speak%20about%20the%20game.%20I%20think%20the%20Indian%20fans%20should%20really%20find%20out%20the%20difference%20between%20people%20taking%20it%20personally%20or%20people%20talking%20about%20his%20cricketing%20side.%20Virat%20really%20appreaciates%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Karthik%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716992640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F09vhqoj8_virat-kohli-dinesh-karthik_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgot-death-threats-for-criticising-virat-kohli-ipl-commentators-shocking-claim-dinesh-karthik-responds-5773051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20RCB's%20wait%20for%20an%20IPL%20title%20continued%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20ended%20the%20season%20as%20the%20highest%20run-getter.%20He%20scored%20741%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%20154.7.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgot-death-threats-for-criticising-virat-kohli-ipl-commentators-shocking-claim-dinesh-karthik-responds-5773051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgot-death-threats-for-criticising-virat-kohli-ipl-commentators-shocking-claim-dinesh-karthik-responds-5773051%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgot-death-threats-for-criticising-virat-kohli-ipl-commentators-shocking-claim-dinesh-karthik-responds-5773051%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hospital%20Dean's%20Big%20Allegation%20Against%20Minister%2C%20MLA%20In%20Pune%20Porsche%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELending%20credence%20to%20allegations%20of%20political%20meddling%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20Pune's%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20has%20claimed%20that%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20accused%20of%20replacing%20the%20blood%20samples%20of%20the%20teenager%20behind%20the%20Porsche%20accident%20had%20been%20made%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forensic%20department%20at%20the%20insistence%20of%20a%20state%20minister%20and%20an%20MLA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislator%2C%20Sunil%20Tingre%2C%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20visiting%20the%20Yerwada%20police%20station%20after%20the%20crash%20-%20in%20which%20two%20IT%20professionals%20were%20killed%20-%20and%20pressuring%20officials%20to%20go%20easy%20on%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20hospital's%20dean%2C%20Vinayak%20Kale%2C%20said%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20and%20Mr%20Tingre%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20and%20asked%20for%20Dr%20Ajay%20Tawade%20to%20be%20made%20the%20head%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital's%20Forensic%20Medicine%20Department.%20Both%20Mr%20Mushrif%20and%20the%20MLA%20are%20from%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Dr%20Kale%20was%20sent%20on%20compulsory%20leave%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfailing%20to%20take%20the%20case%20seriously%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20taking%20proper%20decisions%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20dean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tawade%20and%20Dr%20Shrihari%20Harnor%2C%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital%2C%20had%20been%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20by%20the%20Pune%20Crime%20Branch%20for%20allegedly%20helping%20replace%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20with%20those%20of%20a%20doctor%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20them.%20A%20peon%2C%20Atul%20Ghatkamble%2C%20who%20acted%20as%20the%20middleman%20and%20allegedly%20collected%20the%20Rs%203%20lakh%20bribe%20meant%20for%20the%20two%20doctors%20from%20the%20realtor's%20family%2C%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kale%20said%20Dr%20Tawade%20and%20Mr%20Ghatkamble%20have%20been%20suspended%20while%20the%20contract%20of%20Dr%20Harnor%20has%20been%20terminated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20formed%20for%20the%20investigation%20at%20the%20state%20level%20conducted%20the%20probe%20for%20the%20whole%20day%20yesterday%20(Tuesday).%20I%20have%20taken%20action%20at%20my%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Government%20to%20probe%20the%20alleged%20manipulation%20of%20the%20blood%20sample%2C%20is%20chaired%20by%20Dr%20Pallavi%20Sapale%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20Grant%20Medical%20College%20and%20JJ%20group%20of%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress's%20Allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Maharashtra%20President%2C%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20had%20alleged%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20an%20MLA's%20son%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20accident%20and%20the%20legislator%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20police%20after%20the%20crash%20and%20had%20also%20spoken%20to%20the%20doctors%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20change%20the%20blood%20samples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patole%20had%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20nexus%20between%20the%20police%2C%20politicians%20and%20the%20rich%20and%20influential%20people%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20come%20to%20light%20that%20the%20father%20of%20the%20teenager%2C%20who%20is%20a%20prominent%20builder%20in%20Pune%2C%20had%20communicated%20with%20Dr%20Tawade%20at%20least%2014%20times%20on%20May%2019.%20The%20exchanges%20included%20WhatsApp%2C%20FaceTime%2C%20and%20regular%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20One%20Will%20Be%20Spared'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20accident%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20had%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Pune%20police%20commissioner%20since%20day%20one%20and%20that%20the%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Pune%20police%20commissioner%20since%20day%20one.%20I%20have%20said%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20influential%20the%20person%20is%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20discrimination.%20No%20matter%20how%20rich%20or%20poor%20a%20person%20is%2C%20the%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20no%20one%20will%20be%20spared.%20I%20have%20ordered%20strict%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Accident%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20had%20taken%20place%20around%202.15%20am%20on%20May%2019%2C%20when%20the%2017-year-old%2C%20who%20had%20been%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20two%20pubs%20in%20Pune%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results%2C%20knocked%20down%20the%20two%2024-year-old%20IT%20professionals%20in%20the%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area.%20He%20was%20driving%20a%20Rs%202.5-crore%20Porsche%20at%20over%20150%20kmph.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20the%20bike%2C%20was%20sent%20flying%20and%20hit%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20while%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20-%20who%20was%20riding%20pillion%20-%20was%20flung%2020%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%20Both%20of%20them%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2017%20years%20and%208%20months%20old%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20four%20mon