f%20case%20files%20to%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20landscape%20is%20changing%2C%20slowly%20but%20surely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20understanding%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%20Anchal%20interned%20at%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20chambers%20as%20a%20student.%20She%20remembers%20how%20forthcoming%20they%20were%20with%20respect%20to%20offering%20%E2%80%98Reasonable%20Accommodations%E2%80%99%20to%20help%20her%20work%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20make%20case%20briefs%20with%20page%20number%20references.%20As%20a%20visually-impaired%20person%2C%20it%20is%20sometimes%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20right%20page%20number%2C%20so%20I%20use%20paragraph%20numbers%20instead%20and%20this%20request%20of%20mine%20was%20accommodated%20and%20helped%20me%20better%20do%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%20also%20recollects%20how%20she%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20upon%20completing%20the%20internship%20in%20his%20chamber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20me%20that%20my%20research%20skills%20were%20remarkable%20and%20that%20he%20faced%20no%20challenges%20in%20using%20the%20briefs%20prepared%20by%20me.%20He%20was%20also%20an%20understanding%20senior%20as%20he%20was%20open%20to%20me%20working%20in%20my%20own%20way%20and%20using%20slightly%20different%20formats%20to%20present%20my%20briefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAanchal%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20more%20than%20just%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20triumph%20over%20adversity%2C%20it%20is%20a%20powerful%20call%20to%20action%20for%20building%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20society.%20By%20promoting%20accessibility%20awareness%20and%20implementing%20robust%20support%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20empower%20everyone%20regardless%20of%20ability%20to%20reach%20their%20full%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20just%2