0Sandeep%20rode%20his%20bike%20around%20the%20city%2C%20knocking%20on%20doors%20and%20distributing%20pamphlets.%20He%20also%20carried%20a%20mike%20and%20speaker%20and%20went%20around%20announcing%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Khul%20gaya%2C%20khul%20gaya%2C%20ab%20aapke%20sheher%20mein%20Pizza%20Galleria%20khul%20gaya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pizza%20Galleria%20is%20now%20open%20in%20your%20town%2Fcity)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20practice%20is%20followed%20by%20him%20even%20today.%20Every%20time%20a%20new%20store%20opens%2C%20he%20rides%20around%20the%20city%20shouting%20these%20slogans%2C%20followed%20by%20distributing%20pamphlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED-day%20arrived%20on%2025%20December%202015%2C%20when%20many%20people%20in%20Gohana%20tasted%20their%20first%20fresh-dough%20pizza.%20To%20entice%20customers%2C%20he%20offered%20the%20first%20300%20pizzas%20free%2C%20a%20practice%20followed%20even%20today%20at%20all%20new%20outlets.%20Slowly%20and%20steadily%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20ambience%20and%20novelty%20of%20pizzas%2C%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20was%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20with%20a%20limited%20menu%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20pizzas%2C%20garlic%20bread%2C%20and%20some%20pasta.%20It%20took%20almost%20a%20year%20for%20Sandeep%E2%80%99s%20pizza%20venture%20to%20taste%20success%20in%20Gohana.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20was%20teaching%20people%20to%20try%20a%20new%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20a%20fresh%20dough%20pizza%20or%20even%20how%20to%20eat%20it.%20Just%20like%20me%2C%20they%20too%20thought%20of%20it%20like%20a%20fat%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sauce).%20I%20also%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20food%20was%20perfect%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20experienced%20chefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20by%20building%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20(SOPs)%20to%20be%20followed%20for%20making%20the%20pizzas%2C%20and%20then%20serving%2C%20packing%2C%20and%20delivering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20employment%20in%20small%20towns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Gohana%20accepted%20and%20thronged%20to%20Pizza%20Galleria%2C%20Sandeep%20knew%20he%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20open%20the%20next%20store%20in%20Panipat%20and%20Ganaur%20(Haryana)%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20with%20his%20team%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-500x250.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-768x384.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-150x75.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351209%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandeep%20has%20provided%20employment%20to%20over%20700%20people%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%2072%20stores%2C%20which%20include%20company-owned%20outlets%20as%20well%20as%20franchise%20outlets%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20and%20Chandigarh.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20also%20has%