sed%20rejection%20in%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20Rishabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20while%20pursuing%20computer%20engineering%20at%20the%20Punjabi%20University%2C%20Patiala%2C%20he%20started%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%2C%20which%20offered%20him%20an%20alternate%20way%20to%20serve%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20three%20unsuccessful%20attempts%2C%20I%20finally%20landed%20from%20one%20uniform%20to%20another%20being%20the%20IPS%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20was%20inspired%20to%20serve%20the%20nation%20after%20hearing%20the%20heroic%20tales%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20like%20Tama%20Dora%20and%20Bhagat%20Singh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-4-1716526901-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351054%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERishabh%20was%20inspired%20to%20serve%20the%20nation%20after%20hearing%20the%20heroic%20tales%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20like%20Tama%20Dora%20and%20Bhagat%20Singh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20fourth%20at