0with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20bovines%20usually%20conceive%20in%2037%20to%2040%20months%20if%20it%20is%20malnourished%20but%20when%20you%20provide%20good%20nutrition%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20conceive%20in%2022%20to%2027%20months.%20This%20gives%20farmers%20an%20extra%20cycle%20for%20gestation%20before%20the%20bovine%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20calving.%20Depending%20on%20the%20breed%2C%20they%20earn%20an%20extra%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20to%203%20lakh%20annually%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Manish%20points%20out%20that%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20main%20revenue%20is%20generated%20through%20cattle%20commerce%2C%20genetics%20care%2C%20and%20sales%20through%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274439%2Fagritech-startup-e-feed-helps-cattle-farmers-increase-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20health%20supplements%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Currently%2C%20his%20annual%20revenue%20stands%20at%20Rs%208.72%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20lives%20revolve%20around%20livestock%20and%20we%20have%20proved%20that%20we%20are%20not%20a%20charitable%20organisation.%20We%20are%20a%20viable%20profitable%20business.%20This%20achievement%20is%20too%20big%20for%20a%20PhD%20dropout%20and%20a%20farmer%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20profits%2C%20this%20work%20is%20extremely%20satisfying%20for%20Manish.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20doctors%20cannot%20get%20away%20with%20citing%20unknown%20reasons%20and%20have%20to%20mention%20satisfactory%20reasons%20in%20their%20postmortem%20reports%20so%20that%20farmers%20settle%20insurance%20claims.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20boost%20the%20incomes%20of%20farmer%20families%20by%2040%20percent.%20They%20are%20able%20to%20wed%20their%20daughters%20by%20selling%20good%20b